{
  "stem": "19550.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somewheres in the dark, we were driven to the side of a huge building, where we stood in line in the dark, and the line was moving forward towards one of these men in these stripes, who-- who was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And pretty soon, when I realized what he was doing, I saw that he was shaving the underarm and the pubic hairs of the people, who by then, were told to drop all their clothes in place, so to say, where they were.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] fate-- was a really a fortuitous or serendipitous circumstance, I looked at this young man, and he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we recognized each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had studied together in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he then told me to stay in place, and let everybody come ahead of me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as he was performing his duties, he talked to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the time it became finally my turn, there was nothing that could be known about Auschwitz that I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had already been for four years in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the things that he had told me was that the very important thing was to get out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only way to get out was to be needed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the best way to be needed was to be useful to what was considered the war industry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you're going to have to stop this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's try to ignore his voice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so in turn, I had converted everybody into a mechanic, telling them that when and if the time came where they would ask whatever trade or profession was, they should be mechanics.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
